title: Champion 2.9 - Soccer & Football WordPress Theme
description: Visit us on: https://www.nulledforums.org Champion WordPress Theme was created especially for sport clubs, football clubs, soccer news and sport organizations. The responsive layout is designed based on the Bootstrap 3.1 standards. Please note photos & images are not included in PSD files. Nulled Champion WordPress Theme was built on Visual Composer Page Builder, which is included into the theme. Using Visual Composer you can easily create the pages in Front- or Back-end with 60+ modules. Champion WordPress Theme Features SportsPress Compatible Built with HTML5 and CSS3 Cross-Browser Compatibility: FireFox, Safari, Chrome, IE10+ Live Customizer settings Five Header Styles Revolution Slider included 2 Portfolio Styles: Classic & Masonry Responsive Layout on Bootstrap Parallax and Video Background Mega Main Menu plugin Unlimited Colors 800+ Google Fonts Visual Composer Pagebuilder WooCommerce shop with custom design
